{"tid":1665243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"憂遭警水炮噴濕 示威者幫報紙檔蓋帆布 街坊反勸「你哋走先！」","createTime":"2019-10-20T13:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T13:44:45.000Z","uid":68738,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb9121062cceba94aaf499e9364b18c9a8e57af","tid":1665243,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20191020/720pix/1571573739_63bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20191020%2F720pix%2F1571573739_63bd.jpg&h=ffde0d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在警民衝突烽煙四起的旺角街頭，發生了一件窩心小事。一位戴防毒面罩的示威者，眼見水炮車已經駛至亞皆老街街口，打算協助在附近的報紙檔，替貨物蓋上帆布收檔。現場街訪勸止該示威者，希望她先行離開，「你哋有gear，走先，會有人幫佢㗎喇！」該示威者才撤離。<br />\n<br />\n在過去4個月，示威者幫助市民的善舉不時出現。在8月，灣仔爆發警民衝突，1位伯伯在催淚煙中狀甚痛苦，示威者便上前攙扶該伯伯離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191020/60175905?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191020%2F60175905%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=c2ad1134\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191020%2F60175905%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a0ff438c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191020/60175905?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"25b5c23b10ef94684ff1f832e2a4115bfadb5eaf","tid":1665243,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DD8_tEWp9Ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDD8_tEWp9Ts&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ede81edd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DD8_tEWp9Ts</a><br />\n清真寺民眾Philip Khan怒斥香港政府侮辱伊斯蘭教 <br />\n推爆國際字幕版Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongNewsTV5/status/1185874822384930822?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongNewsTV5%2Fstatus%2F1185874822384930822%3Fs%3D20&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=dad76bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongNewsTV5%2Fstatus%2F1185874822384930822%3Fs%3D20&h=85a8ab0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HongKongNewsTV5/status/1185874822384930822?s=20</a>"}]}